+```
+Technical Specification (TS) – Creative Ideas & Inspiration App
+1. Project Overview
+
+The Creative Ideas & Inspiration App helps users generate, organize, and develop creative ideas for projects, hobbies, writing, art, or problem-solving. It encourages brainstorming, tracks idea progress, and provides prompts and suggestions to spark creativity.
+
+2. Functional Requirements
+2.1 Idea Capture
+
+Users can quickly create new ideas with:
+
+Title / short description
+
+Detailed description or notes
+
+Category or type (e.g., Writing, Art, Design, DIY, Business)
+
+Tags for organization (e.g., “brainstorm”, “urgent”, “inspirational”)
+
+Optional attachments (images, links, sketches, documents)
+
+2.2 Idea Organization
+
+Organize ideas into projects, folders, or boards.
+
+Assign status: “New”, “In Progress”, “Completed”.
+
+Search and filter ideas by category, tag, or date.
+
+2.3 Creative Prompts
+
+Daily or random creative prompts to inspire new ideas.
+
+Prompts can be generated automatically based on user preferences or categories.
+
+Optional AI-generated suggestions for expanding existing ideas.
+
+2.4 Progress Tracking
+
+Track the development of an idea over time.
+
+Add notes, images, or updates for each idea.
+
+Visual timeline or kanban-style board for project progress.
+
+2.5 Sharing & Collaboration
+
+Share ideas or projects with friends, collaborators, or public community (optional).
+
+Commenting or brainstorming together on shared ideas.
+
+Export ideas or boards to PDF or image.
+
+2.6 User Interface
+
+Dashboard showing new ideas, trending ideas, and recently updated projects.
+
+Quick-add button for capturing inspiration immediately.
+
+Drag-and-drop interface for boards or project organization.
+
+Light/Dark mode and customizable themes.
+
+3. Non-Functional Requirements
+3.1 Platform
+
+Mobile (iOS & Android recommended)
+
+Optional web app
+
+3.2 Performance
+
+Quick creation of new idea entries (<1 second).
+
+Smooth navigation between boards, projects, and idea lists.
+
+3.3 Data Storage
+
+Local database (SQLite, Realm, or Hive) for offline access.
+
+Optional cloud sync for multi-device use.
+
+3.4 Security
+
+Protect private ideas with encryption if stored in cloud.
+
+Optional passcode, fingerprint, or face authentication.
+
+3.5 Usability
+
+Intuitive interface optimized for quick idea capture.
+
+Minimal taps to save new ideas or notes.
+
+Easy search and filtering.
+
+4. Technical Stack
+Mobile
+
+Framework: Flutter or React Native
+
+Local database: SQLite, Realm, or Hive
+
+Notifications: native push/local (for prompts or reminders)
+
+Web (Optional)
+
+Frontend: React / Vue.js
+
+Backend: Node.js / Django
+
+Database: PostgreSQL / MongoDB
+
+5. Future Enhancements
+
+AI-powered idea expansion and suggestions.
+
+Mood-based idea prompts (e.g., prompts to spark creativity when stressed).
+
+Gamification: streaks for daily idea creation, achievements for completed projects.
+
+Community sharing and inspiration feed.
+
+Integration with note-taking or drawing apps (e.g., exporting sketches or diagrams).
+```
+
